Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: General Westmoreland libel case
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xjps
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Feb 1985
Vietnam commander General Westmoreland's libel case against CBS ends in stalemate. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less